00:43:00.779 --> 00:43:05.939
So the question this morning, are we standing?

00:43:05.939 --> 00:43:07.779
Are we standing?

00:43:07.779 --> 00:43:09.379
Don't cave in.

00:43:09.379 --> 00:43:10.879
Don't compromise.

00:43:10.879 --> 00:43:12.059
Don't quit.

00:43:12.059 --> 00:43:13.579
Don't give up.

00:43:13.579 --> 00:43:16.459
Stand.

00:43:16.479 --> 00:43:22.839
That you might be able to withstand in the evil day.

00:43:22.839 --> 00:43:26.579
So many things going on in our world today but God's plan

00:43:26.579 --> 00:43:29.559
for his people is clearly explained to us in Ephesians

00:43:29.559 --> 00:43:35.419
chapter number 6 and he's given to us everything we need.

00:43:35.419 --> 00:43:39.859
The provision is there and he wants you and he wants me

00:43:39.859 --> 00:43:41.039
to stand.

00:43:41.039 --> 00:43:41.499
Let's pray.

00:43:41.499 --> 00:43:43.299
Father we love you.

00:43:43.299 --> 00:43:44.499
We thank you for loving us.

00:43:44.499 --> 00:43:46.839
We thank you for the word of God.

00:43:46.839 --> 00:43:50.859
We thank you this morning that we can know your plan for us

00:43:50.859 --> 00:43:52.839
even in this evil day.

00:43:52.839 --> 00:43:55.659
We thank you that you have given us the provision that we

00:43:55.659 --> 00:44:01.179
need and God I pray that you would help us to stand.

00:44:01.179 --> 00:44:04.699
Help us to be bold.

00:44:04.699 --> 00:44:07.299
Help us to have the right position and the right

00:44:07.299 --> 00:44:08.179
disposition.

00:44:08.179 --> 00:44:09.879
Lord help us to honor you.

00:44:09.879 --> 00:44:14.139
Help us to make a difference in our world.

00:44:14.139 --> 00:44:16.619
I pray Father that if there's one here this morning that's

00:44:16.619 --> 00:44:20.059
not sure of heaven, we spoke about that a little bit in the

00:44:20.059 --> 00:44:22.899
beginning of the service, if they're not sure that heaven is

00:44:22.899 --> 00:44:26.579
their home, God I pray that in this moment the Holy Spirit of

00:44:26.579 --> 00:44:30.579
God would convict them of their need for Christ.

00:44:30.579 --> 00:44:32.859
God I pray that we'd have an opportunity to take a Bible and

00:44:32.859 --> 00:44:37.659
show them how they can know for sure that heaven's their home.

00:44:37.659 --> 00:44:41.059
Those that are here that are Christians, Lord as we

00:44:41.059 --> 00:44:43.619
individually evaluate our lives, would you help us to be

00:44:43.619 --> 00:44:49.299
honest about whether we're standing in this evil day,

00:44:49.299 --> 00:44:51.859
whether we're daily putting on the whole armor of God,

00:44:51.859 --> 00:44:54.579
if we're aware of the fact that we're engaged in spiritual

00:44:54.579 --> 00:44:57.379
battle, spiritual warfare.

00:44:57.379 --> 00:45:01.659
God help us every day to put on the whole armor of God.

00:45:01.659 --> 00:45:03.979
I pray that you'd help us to stand and to be strong in the

00:45:03.979 --> 00:45:07.179
power of the Lord.

00:45:07.179 --> 00:45:09.779
I pray God that you'd move and work in this moment as only you

00:45:09.779 --> 00:45:12.139
can and we'll thank you for it in Christ's name we pray.

00:45:12.139 --> 00:45:13.659
Would you stand with me?

00:45:13.659 --> 00:45:14.779
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:45:14.779 --> 00:45:17.059
At the end of our service we have an opportunity to have what

00:45:17.059 --> 00:45:21.139
we call an invitation and what we do simply is invite you to

00:45:21.139 --> 00:45:23.099
respond to God.

00:45:23.099 --> 00:45:25.339
Maybe this morning you're not sure of heaven, we'd never

00:45:25.339 --> 00:45:27.619
embarrass you but if you don't know for sure that heaven is

00:45:27.619 --> 00:45:30.939
your home, if you're a man, Brother Mark is here on my left

00:45:30.939 --> 00:45:33.499
and he has a Bible and he'd show you how you could know for sure

00:45:33.499 --> 00:45:35.019
that heaven is your home.

00:45:35.019 --> 00:45:37.819
If you're a lady, my wife Holly is here on my right and she'll

00:45:37.859 --> 00:45:39.779
take a Bible and show you how you can know for sure that

00:45:39.779 --> 00:45:41.219
heaven is your home.

00:45:41.219 --> 00:45:43.579
Please don't leave here without knowing for sure that heaven is

00:45:43.579 --> 00:45:45.059
your home.

00:45:45.059 --> 00:45:47.819
But then this morning if you're a believer, maybe you just need

00:45:47.819 --> 00:45:51.139
to come and ask God to help you, help you to put on the whole

00:45:51.139 --> 00:45:55.499
armor of God, help you to stand in this evil day.

00:45:55.499 --> 00:45:57.899
However God's spoken to your heart as Kimberly plays,

00:45:57.899 --> 00:45:58.899
the altar is open.

